subchapt er.
(1) Permitted uses and disclosures.    A
covere d entity is per mitted to use or  disclose
protected heal th information as fo llows:
(i) To the individua l;
(ii) For treatment, payment, or health ca re
operations, as pe rmitted by and in compl iance
with § 16 4.506;
(iii) Incident to a use or disclosu re
other wise permi tted or  requir ed by  this
subpart, provided that the co vered e ntity has
