an author izatio n that com plies  with §
164.508;
(v) Pursuant to an ag reement under , or as
other wise permi tted by , § 164.510; a nd
(vi) As pe rmitted by and in compl iance
with this section,  § 164.51 2, or § 164.5 14(e),
(f), or (g).
(2) Required disclosures.   A cov ered entity
is req uired t o discl ose pr otect ed  hea lth
infor mation:
(i) To an i ndivi dual,  when requ ested
under, and as  required by §§ 164 .524 or
