(c) Standard: u ses and dis closures  of
protected  health infor mation sub ject to an
agreed upon r estrict ion.  A cov ered entity
that has agreed to a restric tion pursuan t to §
164.522(a) (1) may  not use  or dis close  the
prote cted he alth inf ormati on cov ered by the
